flowchart TD
    %% Roles & Entry Points
    A[User / Student Accesses Landing Page] --> B{Choose Action}

    %% Pathway 1: Report Item
    B -->|Report Lost/Found Item| C[Fill Item Report Form]
    C --> D{Form Input Valid?}
    D -->|No| E[Show Inline Validation Errors]
    E --> C
    D -->|Yes| F[Save Record to LocalStorage]
    F --> G[Display Confirmation Toast Message]
    G --> H[Redirect to Status Tracker / Catalog]

    %% Pathway 2: Search & Claim
    B -->|Search/Browse Items| I[View Item Catalog]
    I --> J[Apply Keyword Search / Category Filters]
    J --> K[View Filtered List of Items]
    K --> L[Click Item for Detail View]
    L --> M{Wish to Claim?}
    M -->|No| I
    M -->|Yes| N[Submit Claim Request with Verification Info]
    N --> O[Save Claim State as 'Pending' in LocalStorage]
    O --> P[Display Claim Tracking Status]

    %% Pathway 3: Admin Management
    B -->|Admin Access| Q[Open Admin Panel]
    Q --> R[Review Pending Item Claims & Reports]
    R --> S{Verify Proof of Ownership?}
    S -->|Rejected| T[Update Status to 'Claim Rejected']
    S -->|Approved| U[Update Status to 'Returned / Closed']
    T --> V[Sync Status Update to LocalStorage & Dashboard Metrics]
    U --> V
    V --> W[Update Summary Dashboard Analytics]
